  * Team upload

  [ Debian Janitor ]
  * Bump debhelper from old 11 to 12.
  * Set debhelper-compat version in Build-Depends.
  * Set upstream metadata fields: Bug-Database, Bug-Submit, Repository,
    Repository-Browse.
  * Remove constraints unnecessary since stretch:
    + Build-Depends: Drop versioned constraint on node-tap, node-graceful-fs.
    + node-fs-write-stream-atomic: Drop versioned constraint on nodejs,
      node-graceful-fs in Depends.
  * Remove constraints unnecessary since buster:
    + Build-Depends: Drop versioned constraint on node-iferr, node-imurmurhash
      and nodejs.
    + node-fs-write-stream-atomic: Drop versioned constraint on node-iferr and
      node-imurmurhash in Depends.
  * Bump debhelper from old 12 to 13.

